1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,375
Every Sunday, the world gets a little quieter. And we build.

2
00:00:03,375 --> 00:00:06,750
One idea. One weekend. What could go wrong?

3
00:00:06,750 --> 00:00:10,125
Prototypes don't need to be perfect. They need to be real.

4
00:00:10,125 --> 00:00:13,500
By sunset, something that didn't exist — does.

5
00:00:13,500 --> 00:00:16,875
Sundai. Ship something new. See you next Sunday.
